
[3] REPE CMPBKW odd-address slope (expect 22/rep):
  CW=1: REP F 2 + insn 33 = 35
  CW=2: REP F 2 + insn 55 = 57
  CW=3: REP F 2 + insn 77 = 79
  totals=[35, 57, 79] slopes=[22, 22] -> 7+22/rep layout reading CONFIRMED

